brandComInfo.introduce:
ABOUT
    For our team, design is a way of life – a professional philosophy, a creative rallying, and a shared purpose in support of excellence. Our global experience pays tribute to the passionate creation of distinctive, innovative, and inspiring environments. Working in conjunction with nature to achieve impressive results with enduring appeal, we design outdoor spaces that are timeless, never forced – and establish relationships that strengthen these concepts for future projects and generations. With an eye toward holistic development, land preservation, and aesthetic cognizance, our designers improve the relationship between people and place. We graciously accept our role as stewards of the land and the built environment with the full creativity, integrity, and the commitment of our entire worldwide team.
        After nearly 10 years, our commitment remains the same – to ensure people thrive in beautiful, functional surroundings by delivering quality-designed projects. We are honored to serve the profession, our clients, and people around the globe by creating spaces that are enjoyed and celebrated by the world’s communities. We continue to be inspired by opportunities to create venues that serve as markers of history and catalysts for thoughtful design.
简介
       对我们的团队来说，设计是一种生活方式——一门职业哲学、一场创意拉力赛以及追求卓越过程中的一个共同目标。我们全球化的经验让我们对于创造的独特、创新和鼓舞人心的景观环境而感到致敬。通过让我们的设计融入大自然来创造出具有持久吸引力的经典作品，我们设计的户外环境是自然的，永恒的，并且我们会和自然建立关系来帮助为未来的项目和后世人强化这个理念。通过着眼于整体发展、土地资源保护和审美认知，我们的设计师在改善人与自然的关系。我们欣然接受土地管理者的角色，并承诺以充分的创造力、诚信和整个全球团队的承诺来设计环境。虽已历经近 10 年，我们的承诺始终如初——通过交付有质量的设计项目来确保人们能在集美丽和功能于一体的环境中生活。通过创造受到世界各地的喜爱和赞扬的空间环境，我们很荣幸能为我们的行业、客户和全球的人们提供服务。
